When invoked, the Resilum container additionally launches and
distributes binaries from the following projects, each under its own
upstream license:

  * Reticulum Network Stack          MIT
  * rns-covert-transport (TechVoid)  Apache-2.0
  * rns-over-icmp (matvik22000)      (no declared license — used as-is)
  * iodine                           ISC
  * i2pd                             BSD-3-Clause
  * Tor + obfs4proxy                 BSD
  * yggdrasil-go                     LGPL-3.0
  * Meshtastic Python                Apache-2.0 / GPL-3.0

Each component is invoked as a separate process, not statically
linked, so the bundle as a whole is distributed as a mere aggregation.
